title: Facebook’s photo transfer tool opens to more users in Europe, LatAm and Africa
text: Facebook is continuing to open up access to a data porting tool it launched in Ireland in December.

title: Early Facebook executive Chamath Palihapitiya predicts what a 'Big Tech' break up would look like
text: "If the regulator's efforts are successful, Big Tech will be broken up within the decade," Palihapitiya said.

title: Facebook is not only exposed to travel but to retail and entertainment sectors due to coronavirus
text: Laura Martin, analyst at Needham, joins 'Closing Bell' to discuss the impact of the coronavirus on tech.

title: FANG Stocks Lose Nearly $150B In A Day As Coronavirus Fears Rise Even More, Oil Crashes
text: The "FANG" technology companies, known for their impressive growth in the last two decades, took a beating on Monday as markets opened after a turbulent weekend.
